      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example delivers power through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been executed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The suspension geometry is maintained via refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability expected of this platform. While the aesthetic reflects its status as a driven machine, the drivetrain remains tight and the power delivery is linear across the entire 8,000 RPM sweep.",
