    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi S5 Sportback in Navarra Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been my pride and joy, always garaged and hand-washed. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though it shows a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and one small graze on the rear passenger wheel rim, consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the Magma Red fine Nappa leather remains supple; there is very slight creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but the cabin is otherwise pristine, odor-free, and features the original floor mats. Every piece of technology, from the Audi Virtual Cockpit to the Bang & Olufsen 3D sound system, functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a complete service record from authorized dealerships. We recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a brake fluid flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the engine pulls cleanly through the entire rev range. This is a turn-key performance luxury vehicle for a buyer who values an honest, well-cared-for machine.",
